summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Second Avenue Northwest from West Sixtieth Street to the north line of the Electric Motor Line Addition in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing same under Ordinance No. 20422, creating Local Improvement District No. 2017 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
